Buh-bye now.

567
00:36:30,521 --> 00:36:32,091
Are we in trouble?

568
00:36:32,190 --> 00:36:34,033
Please. It's all
under control.

569
00:36:37,328 --> 00:36:40,036
So, you really
Mr. Wolf's kids?

570
00:36:40,431 --> 00:36:41,569
Yep.

571
00:36:41,899 --> 00:36:43,845
Hmm. Interesting.

572
00:36:43,901 --> 00:36:45,847
