for Highcroft Electronics.

576
00:36:53,244 --> 00:36:55,781
The hotel, they called the
company to arrange the limo.

577
00:36:56,180 --> 00:36:57,215
Uh-oh.

578
00:36:57,582 --> 00:36:58,720
Yeah. Uh-oh.

579
